\begin_inset Formula $(-1)^{n}>-n$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $n>1$
\end_inset

.
 Therefore,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
n+\frac{(-1)^{n}}{n}>n-1>1-1=0
\]

\end_inset

and hence 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

